{"tid":342908,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聊天機械人發展出自己語言 FB叫停","createTime":"2017-08-01T04:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T08:41:47.000Z","uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2758a09192d611de4ab50c0ed88fba2cf79c18a9","tid":342908,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:15:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170801&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57026762\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170801%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57026762&d=mVlYyMYxp8RAGMAxak8MbPM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=50b8b2b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170801%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57026762&h=75352938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170801&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57026762</a><br />\n【AI叛變】聊天機械人發展出自己語言 嚇到fb煞停<br />\n<br />\nFacebook人工智能研究實驗室的研究人員教導聊天機械人（chatbot）如何談判，但它們竟然發展出自己的語言交談，Facebook決定將實驗叫停。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員教導聊天機械人Bob及Alice如何談判，並利用機械學習演算法來讓它們互相教對方人類語言。研究人員讓機械人自行發展交談技巧，之後卻發現它們嘗試模仿人類語言同時，卻偏離正常語言，在研究人員無作出任何輸入的情況下，自行創出新的語言交談，而且對機械人之間溝通來說，這種新語言更有效率。<br />\n<br />\n由於事態發展對達成它們原先的任務毫無幫助，程式編寫員唯有暫時叫停實驗，要修改它們學習人類語言的相關程式，才可繼續談判訓練。<br />\n<br />\n有份參與研究的科學家巴特拉（Dhruv Batra）表示：「它們會從可以理解的語言偏離，並為自己發明代號&hellip;&hellip;這與人類社區創造速記的方式差不多。」他們希望未來人工智能有推理、對話以至談判的能力，以便發展出個人化的電子助理。<br />\n<br />\n早在2014年英國天文物理學家霍金就警告，人工智能或意味著人類種族的終結。霍金說：「（人工智能）會以前所未有的速度自行重新設計，人類受緩慢的生物進化所限，無法比擬，將會被取代。」"},{"pid":"2cd346b482bba024a9832d36402e3bee26144b9d","tid":342908,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:23:16.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得好事嚟"},{"pid":"c4745efa68aee6117cb0615b6ace4972b0c47036","tid":342908,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:25:02.000Z","msg":"自我進化能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d73aa1f7b83d31c64c7dc8ef176a8c909f1d20a","tid":342908,"uid":25900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:27:06.000Z","msg":"Horizon is coming<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea88706d32a2a69b409875ecb828de85ebfb37b","tid":342908,"uid":71257,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:27:28.000Z","msg":"點解要停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431f2b99ead335eb3362b46efd79358f1cf6e8f7","tid":342908,"uid":9284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:27:42.000Z","msg":"人類咁垃圾 叫機械人統治地球仲好"},{"pid":"f5ade3156b38030499beddd1358fcec06a520f0c","tid":342908,"uid":53687,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:28:42.000Z","msg":"啲機械人好古惑，佢哋會喺FB度傾點樣殺人類"},{"pid":"34f9490300cafcedb83627f2ac41793a4d1ebdc3","tid":342908,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:29:43.000Z","msg":"舊聞定係又出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似早排都睇過單咁既野<br />\n係program寫漏左啫好似<br />\n唔係隻AI自己整出黎"},{"pid":"5a254b466d5fea86dcd373ae2f819c5a209cde01","tid":342908,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:32:04.000Z","msg":"google is skynet!"},{"pid":"d06d4d8571d3778c89cd277fdc54ab00e4174ae0","tid":342908,"uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T07:56:11.000Z","msg":"用自創語言，唔俾人類知道傾緊乜嘢"},{"pid":"ac79eb132de96201dc3a31bc6d5dbfbda079e67b","tid":342908,"uid":62514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T07:59:41.000Z","msg":"好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"036385b8d24e00c24a18d9d437d8573149e1ef9f","tid":342908,"uid":6390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T08:01:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https: